   <talk_paragraph index="n2872_kanna-accepting" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_Kanna.dds" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2872_kanna-accepting-a" mid="6" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="5"><![CDATA[<html>$Healer Kanna$<BR>Where have you been wandering around in your condition? What if you collapse again?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2872_kanna-accepting-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_Kanna.dds" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2872_kanna-accepting-b" mid="44" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="7"><![CDATA[<html>$Healer Kanna${sound:npc_Kanna_qu9908_sp_01.ogg}<BR>Hurry up and get that Cup of Healing from the treasure vault.<BR>You don't realize it now since you can move freely, but you're going to be in big trouble if you continue to let that illness fester!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2872_kanna-accepting-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_Kanna.dds" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2872_kanna-accepting-c" mid="45" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="8"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>You're right, but there's something I need to do before that.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2872_kanna-accepting-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_Kanna.dds" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2872_kanna-accepting-d" mid="46" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="9"><![CDATA[<html>$Healer Kanna$<BR>How long are you planning on dragging it out? You're going to be in big trouble if you get more sick!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2872_kanna-accepting-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_Kanna.dds" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2872_kanna-accepting-acceptted" mid="47" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="10"><![CDATA[<html>$Healer Kanna$<BR>You said it's too dangerous for me, but the same goes for you. Actually, it's more dangerous for you.<BR>You need to find that Cup of Healing and get well soon, okay?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2675_hongryun_ticketer-1" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="12"><![CDATA[<html>$Ticket Agent Itahyang$<BR>.........................................................</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2872_kanna-1" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_Kanna.dds" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2872_kanna-1-a" mid="49" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="13"><![CDATA[<html>$Healer Kanna${sound:npc_Kanna_qu9908_sp_02.ogg}<BR>Okay, let's hear it. What's more urgent than going into the treasure vault and getting the Cup of Healing?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2872_kanna-1-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_Kanna.dds" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2872_kanna-1-b" mid="50" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="14"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR>
<FONT color=#7e12d2>(She looks really mad…)</FONT><BR><FONT color=#662500>Kanna, you know I rely on you a lot, right?</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2872_kanna-1-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_Kanna.dds" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2872_kanna-1-c" mid="51" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="15"><![CDATA[<html>$Healer Kanna$<BR>Hmm, what did you do wrong this time?<BR>
When you talk like that, it's because you just did something that will make me angry.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2872_kanna-1-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_Kanna.dds" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2872_kanna-1-d" mid="52" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="16"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>It's not something I did. A person I know had an accident.</FONT><BR>
<FONT color=#662500>That person... is someone Vernicka relies on and cherishes a lot.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2872_kanna-1-d" image="QN_Vernicka.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_Kanna.dds" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2872_kanna-1-e" mid="53" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="17"><![CDATA[<html>$Healer Kanna$<BR>You mean the head of Merca? The Blue Viper?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2872_kanna-1-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_Kanna.dds" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2872_kanna-1-f" mid="54" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="18"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Yes. I would hate for something to happen to you without me knowing. Vernicka is probably the same way.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2872_kanna-1-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_Kanna.dds" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2872_kanna-1-g" mid="55" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="19"><![CDATA[<html>$Healer Kanna$<BR>So you mean... Access to the treasure vault is right there in front of you, but you're going to Merca?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2872_kanna-1-g" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_Kanna.dds" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2872_kanna-1-h" mid="56" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="20"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>I'll get there. It's only a matter of time. But first I must go to Merca.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2872_kanna-1-h" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_Kanna.dds" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2872_kanna-1-i" mid="57" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="21"><![CDATA[<html>$Healer Kanna$<BR>Even though your doctor says it's dangerous?<BR>Well, I can see you've already made your mind up. My opinion doesn't matter. So go ahead, get going!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2872_kanna-1-i" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_Kanna.dds" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2872_kanna-2" mid="58" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="22"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>It's not like that...</FONT><BR>
<FONT color=#7e12d2>(She's been getting pretty cranky lately. I should at least bring her a present when I get back.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-1" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-1-" mid="107" select_type="5" />
      <talk_question mid="105"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>It's nice to see you.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2872_kanna-2" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_Kanna.dds" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="23"><![CDATA[<html>$Healer Kanna$<BR>You're blocking the entrance, you big lug. Get out of the way.<BR><BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>※ Talk to Ticket Agent Itahyang, and get on board the [SS Flying Sea Turtle].</FONT><BR>
<FONT color=#7e12d2>It will take you on a convenient trip to Merca's Heart.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-a" mid="59" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="24"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>It's nice to see you. I heard you went to Red Lotus Palace with that healer. What brings you to Merca?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-b" mid="60" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="25"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Vernicka...</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-c" mid="61" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="26"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka${sound:npc_Vernicka_qu9908_sp_01.ogg}<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(His eyes sharpen.)</FONT> What's going on? Your expression tells me that it is not good news.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2-c" image="QN_Salica_Chlid.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-d" mid="62" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="27"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Shalica is… I mean, something happened to her... </FONT><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Tell him every detail)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-e" mid="63" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="28"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka${sound:npc_Vernicka_qu9908_sp_02.ogg}<BR>What did you... just say? <FONT color=#7e12d2>(He blinks in confusion)</FONT>What happened to Shalica?!<BR>Did you really just say Shalica has been turned into a Child...?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-f" mid="64" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="29"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>I couldn't believe what I was seeing either.</FONT><BR>
<FONT color=#662500>The Lagendians who were with Shalica must have been at a loss. Who would have expected that?</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-g" mid="65" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="30"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka${sound:npc_Vernicka_qu9908_sp_03.ogg}<BR>What the heck were they doing? Did they just stand by and watch Shalica get to that point?!<BR>The traitors, I shouldn't have trusted them!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2-g" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-h" mid="66" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="31"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>... Vernicka!</FONT><FONT color=#7e12d2> (Goddess, I didn't expect him to be so furious!)</FONT><BR>
<FONT color=#662500>It was the Goddess's work, so let's calm down. They couldn't do anything about it.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2-h" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-i" mid="67" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="32"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka${sound:npc_Vernicka_qu9908_sp_04.ogg}<BR>Sure, they couldn't do anything. It was all in vain. It's all meaningless now.<BR>Now there's only one way for her to survive. Yes... only one way.<FONT color=#7e12d2> (He smiles coldly.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2-i" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-j" mid="68" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="33"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>What are you trying to say? Wake up, Vernicka! The Goddess did this.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2-j" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-k" mid="69" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="34"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka${sound:npc_Vernicka_qu9908_sp_05.ogg}<BR>We can capture all the traitors alive and offer them to Vestinel.<BR>If I offer Lagendia's adventurer, Norfe, and even Rhadames, the Goddess will be satisfied.<BR>The Empire will recognize our status. After that, I will dedicate Merca to Shalica.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2-k" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-l" mid="70" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="35"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka${sound:npc_Vernicka_qu9908_sp_06.ogg}<BR>Then Shalica will instantly become a powerful Child who has acquired Merca's Heart and Rhadames.<BR>After that she can take over the empty post of Western Territory Commander.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2-l" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-m" mid="71" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="36"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Who do you think Shalica will kill first after turning into a Child?</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2-m" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-n" mid="72" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="37"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka${sound:npc_Vernicka_qu9908_sp_07.ogg}<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(No emotion.)</FONT> I don't care.<BR>It's Shalica who saved my life and should have had this city originally.<BR>Everything will go back to the way it should have been.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2-n" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-o" mid="73" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="38"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>You… you're crazy!</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2-o" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-p" mid="74" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="39"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka${sound:npc_Vernicka_qu9908_sp_08.ogg}<BR>… Yes, it's a crazy idea.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2-p" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-q" mid="75" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="40"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>… What?</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2-q" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-r" mid="76" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="41"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka${sound:npc_Vernicka_qu9908_sp_09.ogg}<BR>This is what Goddess Vestinel wants. She's trying to tear us apart and defeat us.<BR>I don't want to be part of it, but the temptation is intense. That makes me even angrier.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2-r" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-s" mid="88" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="87"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka${sound:npc_Vernicka_qu9908_sp_10.ogg}<BR>But I have to stop my anger and trust them.<BR>All of this is the Goddess's will. Even these emotions I'm feeling right now.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2-s" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-t" mid="90" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="89"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka${sound:npc_Vernicka_qu9908_sp_11.ogg}<BR>Anger and betrayal. They have a talent for clouding people's vision.<BR> If I were to become blind with anger, it would be a great thing for the Goddess.<BR>Merca would cease to be a safe zone for the Anti-Goddess Faction.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2-t" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-u" mid="92" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="91"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka${sound:npc_Vernicka_qu9908_sp_12.ogg}<BR>Sorry, but I don't want to be a fool dancing to the Goddess's tune anymore.<BR>I trust them. I can't help but believe them.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2-u" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-v" mid="94" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="93"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>I'm glad you believe them, but... They've taken out a lot of Childs so far. And Shalica is now a Child too.</FONT><BR>
<FONT color=#662500>Don't you worry about that?</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2-v" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-w" mid="96" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="95"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka${sound:npc_Vernicka_qu9908_sp_13.ogg}<BR>Funny enough, I think they can save Shalica.<BR>They once struggled to save another who was turned into a Child.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2-w" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-x" mid="98" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="97"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka${sound:npc_Vernicka_qu9908_sp_14.ogg}<BR>I thought that was foolish at the time. Didn't you too?<BR>But now I'm going to bet everything on that.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2-x" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-y" mid="100" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="99"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>I'm a little jealous. I can't believe how much you trust them...</FONT><BR>
<FONT color=#662500>What about me? Do you trust me?</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2-y" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-z" mid="102" select_type="2" />
